Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此 也不是完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的身高体格来判断的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H313131&\3c&HEDEDED&\pos(1232,280)}年龄身体测定的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H313131&\3c&HEDEDED&\pos(1656,365)}重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H313131&\3c&HEDEDED&\pos(1664,551)}轻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H313131&\3c&HEDEDED&\pos(1686,998)}黑仪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平均体重应该是四十五公斤以上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是实际的体重是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是初中毕业 进入这所高中之前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到了一只螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体重被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就算你不理解也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为被胡乱猜测的话过于麻烦 所以才说的
