Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.09,0:25:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是月火
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.98,0:25:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然叫做工蚁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.18,0:25:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么叫的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.02,0:25:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有两成是在工作的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.97,0:25:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的八成不干活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.78,0:25:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要提意见
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.01,0:25:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.51,0:25:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工蚁这种名字本来就是强加于人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.67,0:25:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在操纵别人的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.60,0:25:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 又不能叫做偷懒蚂蚁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.29,0:25:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来是预告片谜题
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.76,0:25:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谜题
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.19,0:25:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到Hit and Beat那就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.82,0:25:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是火怜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.57,0:25:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个and表示的记号该怎么念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.73,0:25:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是问题难 是问题文让人搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.69,0:25:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.32,0:25:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是&吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.16,0:25:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不通啊
